data.description: Motivated Seller!! Back on market @ no fault of home.  Stunning 12 acre estate w/ panoramic Cascade views & endless possibilities for equestrian enthusiasts. Property fully fenced & x-fenced, w/ horse stalls, tack room, hay storage, lrg shop-perfect for RV storage & supplies & circular driveway. Mature landscaping, 3 bed 2 bath w/ spacious primary bedroom & huge bonus room. Lrg windows throughout w/ stunning Cascade Mt. views. 1.5 mi from Brasada Ranch, 14 mi. to Redmond, & 19 mi. to Bend.
